{"tid":1612031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"遠距離水魔法整合","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:03:19.000Z","uid":324194,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6d47db2edbeff8332913ae6b00b94ec4a232d30f","tid":1612031,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"整合一下 水魔法POST既建議<br />\n不分勇武和理非都能玩<br />\n<br />\n彈弓<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-3jCwDFXHVY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-3jCwDFXHVY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=98c7ed5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-3jCwDFXHVY&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n棍網球︳袋棍球︳Lacrosse<br />\n要練習要D技巧  但解決左用手掉唔夠遠既問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxoYNrD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxoYNrD.jpg&h=6b92df21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rjv8qdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjv8qdj.jpg&h=a7860ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個準繩度太低<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2JEQy9NdYEM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2JEQy9NdYEM&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=ddea7e26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2JEQy9NdYEM</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n (玩具水槍射程太短不予考慮)<br />\n真要玩水槍既話..........就洗車用既...呢個攞黎射顏料有冇得諗<br />\n0:50 注意 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iq7aqvi088U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIq7aqvi088U&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=3bfba754\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iq7aqvi088U</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">需要大量人手製造彈藥</span></span><br />\n水魔法製作&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【水魔法師召換】Last Minute話你知聽日點玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1606828/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1606828/</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【Wizard of Legend】水魔法師攻略整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1607795/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1607795/</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45a6c23a596bdac98b8c1ad4dde7370d7c26a673","tid":1612031,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"408100618147f35ac7c6807b312f2491adffd986","tid":1612031,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6a1ef6af6eef9e7f683be54daa571298b0480c9","tid":1612031,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef01b0f2b8e100cfe4cb644296715e0ae49f3d92","tid":1612031,"uid":6674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JSD9gYgVuvE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJSD9gYgVuvE&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a2b938ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JSD9gYgVuvE</a>"},{"pid":"f315aa3db5ea298349284b6645a91a9d517c86b2","tid":1612031,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:27:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"672c963e33d2ea7d3cf502f4325cd6228fcfb10e","tid":1612031,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afd4587da9c9200c174e07e2efa2153ac735f449","tid":1612031,"uid":283006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">（發夢必修）整過同未試過整水彈嘅手足都入一入黎</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h